%term _ progress<< (ofstack/frame (offrame/fluid-bind _ _) TK) TE Dv (nstuck/step step/fletr) %.
%[[ Note: when I write in ``eqtm E (tm/susp E)`` here and then
try to check the case, the error I get is worrisome, occurs-check wise. %]]
%sort p3 {_ eqtm E (tm/susp E')} {K} {Dv} {_ step (<< (f/unsusp --- ; K) E Dv) S'} %.
