	%<- (invf-app2 (%the (ofstack (f/app2 (tm/lam T' E) V --- ; K) Ta Bs) TK) (%the (subset Bs Cs) Sub) (%the (of (tm/lam T' E) (ty/arrow Ta Tb) Cs) T1) (%the (ofstack K Tb Cs) TK''))
	%<- (inv-lam T1 (%the (eqty (ty/arrow Ta Tb) (ty/arrow T' T'')) Eq) (%the ({x} %pi (of x T' #) %-> (of (E x) T'' #)) Tfunc))
	%<- (p3 Eq TK'' Tfunc TE2' Ans) %.
